high_descs: turn right, walk to the white table on the left
grab the apple from the table
turn left, turn left, walk to the microwave
open the microwave, put the apple in, heat the apple, take the apple
turn right, walk to the refrigerator
put the apple in the refrigerator
anns.task_desc: cook the apple in the microwave, put it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Walk to the table to your left.
Pick up the apple from the front of the table.
Turn around and walk across the kitchen to reach the stove.
Warm the apple in the microwave above the stove, then take it out again.
Turn around, turn left, and walk to the fridge.
Place the apple on the top shelf of the fridge, to the left of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Take a half step forward then turn right and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the wall and then turn left.
Pick up the apple in front of you.
Turn left and walk until you clear the counter to your left then turn left and walk to the stove you see in front of and to the left of you and stand facing it.
Cook the apple in the microwave and then get it back out and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the fridge and stand in front of it facing it.
Put the apple in the fridge and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple in the fridge.
